    <string name="perm_dialog_title">Network &amp; Privacy</string>
    <string name="perm_dialog_msg">KlippShell requires network access to establish a direct interface with your printer\'s Moonraker API, as well as notification permissions to send you critical alerts and print milestones (e.g., print completed or error) while you watch TV or use other apps. An internet connection is required for OTA update checks, providing status assets for the Android TV Launcher, and for advanced companion features. Data security is our top priority: communication takes place exclusively locally between your device and the printer. No control or telemetry data is transmitted to external servers.</string>
